        The galaxy is being corrupted by dark matter. 
        There is no hope. We must find a new home. 
        
        We know of a ancient portal to another galaxy 
        orbiting a green super giant star in the Milky 
        way. You must find it. It requires a series of 
        alien artifacts to open, find them all. 
        
